Super admin creation process from fresh install
Install process
admin creation
revamp index.php to advertise all shows that are being run through RBS
add in admin tiers

if admin_login has production var then go straight there



Quick with internet:
sql schema has default values for fields
sanatise login inputs
post through headers for admin_login error messages


Scripting:
grep command that allows you to vim open right at the results

Admin register
 1. User signs up on another admins account
 2. Admin emails out request to users, uniq url
    2.a User doesn't exist, they get an email to create new account with admin powers
    2.b User already exists, admin gets the option to upgrade them to admin, they get notification email.
